: code = Unknown desc`)\n  - High frequency failures (e.g., 1136 occurrences in case of `frontend-1`)\n\n#### **Hypotheses Based on Evidence**\n1. **Frontend Services Failing to Retrieve Ads**\n   - Component: `adservice`\n   - Reason: `RPC failed due to backend instability (\"AdService-getRandomAds-exception\")`\n     - This issue likely caused the `frontend` service requests to return errors.\n   - Evidence:\n     - Logs from `frontend` contain entries such as: `failed to get ads: rpc error: code = Unknown desc`\n     - Frequent association with specific RPC paths across pods.\n\n2. **Backend Adservice's Internal Failure**\n   - Component: `adservice`\n   - Reason: `Byteman dynamic instrumentation failure`\n     - This further corresponds to logs like `attempting to load Byteman agent more than once`.\n   - Evidence: Strong concentration of Byteman rule and transformation injection logs in `adservice`.\n\n---\n\n### Final JSON Output\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"rpc error\",\n    \"Unknown desc\",\n    \"java.lang.Error: Injected error\",\n    \"AdService-getRandomAds-exception-1749460243\",\n    \"Byteman agent\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"RPC failure likely associated with 'AdService-getRandomAds-exception' instability.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"RPC error detected in frontend, frequent failures correlating with adservice instability.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Instrumented backend failed due to Byteman agent configuration errors.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Injected error observed linked to Byteman rule and dynamic triggers.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n后续步骤:\n- 根据 AdService 的根因进行更深入的排查，可能需要检查 \"Byteman\" 动态插装系统或升级服务端稳定性。"}
