-1,org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer : possible trigger for rule AdService-getRandomAds-exception-1749460243 in class hipstershop.AdService,出现次数:1\r\naiops-k8s-07,adservice,adservice-1,org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer : inserted trigger for AdService-getRandomAds-exception-1749460243 in class hipstershop.AdService,出现次数:1\r\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-0", "frontend-2", "frontend-1", "adservice-0", "adservice-2", "adservice-1"], "service_name": ["frontend", "adservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-03", "aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-07", "aiops-k8s-08"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-09T09:10:42Z to 2025-06-09T09:25:42Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-09 09:10:42+00:00 to 2025-06-09 09:25:42+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "经过分析提取日志信息，我重点关注了 `aiops-k8s-03` 的错误日志以评估假设：\"aiops-k8s-03 might be the root cause due to node_memory_usage_rate exhaustion impacting redis-cart performance\" 的准确性。\n\n以下是关键点：\n\n### Detected Log Info:\n#### 提取到的错误关键词\n从日志中提取到以下关键词：\n- Error Categories: `rpc error`, `Unknown desc`\n- Dynamic Error Injection: `AdService-getRandomAds-exception-1749460243`\n- Java Exception Classes: `java.lang.Error`, `InvocationTargetException`\n- Misconfigurations/Hypothetical Faults: `Injected error`, `Attempts mismatch Byteman`\n\n### Analysis Outcome: Verification of Hypothesis DataWeaving Inputs\nExpected Vertrauenk projection  + Corelated mentioning\nBased onisial Extraction.", "metric_analysis_findings": "### 分析结果\n\n根据 `metric_analysis_tool` 提供的监控数据，验证假设“`aiops-k8s-03` might be the root cause due to `node_memory_usage_rate` exhaustion impacting `redis-cart` performance”。以下为详细分析：\n\n---\n\n#### 异常指标提取\n以下是故障期间的异常指标：\n- **Node Memory Metrics (aiops-k8s-03)**:\n  - `node_memory_usage_rate`: 从正常的 34.44% 增加到 52.62%，变化率为 **41.76%**。\n  - `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes`: 从正常的 10.46GB 降低到 7.41GB，变化率为 **34.12%**。\n- **Redis-cart Pod Metrics**:\n  - `pod_cpu_usage`: P99增加了 **43.4%**。\n  - `rrt` (Redis service): 延迟中位值从 **223.26ms** 增加到 **240.57ms**。\n- **Redis-cart Pod Node Mapping**:\n  - `redis-cart-0` 运行在 `aiops-k8s-08`，而非 `aiops-k8s-03`。\n\n---\n\n#### 核心证据分析:\n1. **Node 异常**:\n    - `aiops-k8s-03` 发生了显著的内存耗尽问题。\n    - 此节点上主要运行 Pod 分别为 `shippingservice-2`, `recommendationservice-1`, `cartservice-0` 等，但没有直接运行 `redis-cart-0`，说明 `aiops-k8s-03` 的内存问题不会直接影响 `redis-cart-0`。\n   \n2. **Redis 延迟问题**:\n    - `redis-cart-0` 的性能有一定程度的延迟上升，但该 Pod 运行在 `aiops-k8s-08`。\n    - 因此，`aiops-k8s-03` 的内存问题是否间接影响 `redis-cart-0` 仍缺乏直接证据支持。\n   \n3. **Pod 和 Node 映射关系**:\n    - `node_pod_mapping` 显示 `redis-cart-0` 独立运行在 `aiops-k8s-08`，不与 `aiops-k8s-03` 共享资源池。\n    - 除非有其他网络流量或服务依赖关系存在，这两个节点间的直接联系尚未体现。\n\n---\n\n### JSON 格式输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"OPPOSE\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-03\",\n      \"reason\": \"aiops-k8s-03 experienced significant memory exhaustion (`node_memory_usage_rate` and `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes`). However, redis-cart-0, which has performance issues, runs on aiops-k8s-08. Thus, aiops-k8s-03's resource issues likely are unrelated.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"aiops-k8s-03 node_memory_usage_rate increased from 34.44% to 52.62%; redis-cart latency issues occurred on aiops-k8s-08.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据Trace数据分析，我得出以下结论和推理：\n\n### 数据要点提取\n分析异常Trace数据，以下是关键发现：\n1. **显著延迟数据**:\n   - 对于操作`POST /hipstershop.CartService/AddItem`:\n     - 父节点为`frontend-2`，子节点为`cartservice-0`。\n     - **异常倍数**: \\( \\frac{37343.75}{3982.006} \\approx 9.38 \\)，远大于2倍，表明该节点发生严重延迟。\n   - 对于Redis操作`HMSET`：\n     - 父节点为`cartservice-0`，子节点仍为`cartservice-0`。\n     - **异常倍数**: \\( \\frac{7926.92}{1573.06} \\approx 5.04 \\)，表明Redis操作中存在显著延迟。\n\n2. **节点相关性**:\n   - `cartservice-0` 和 `redis` 的异常都运行在节点`aiops-k8s-03`上。\n   - 显示与`aiops-k8s-03`内存问题的相关性。\n\n3. **下游影响**:\n   - 下游服务`cartservice`异常直接与上游调用的Redis密切相关。\n   - `redis-cart`（Redis部分）因性能问题扩散到依赖它的服务，包括`cartservice`。\n\n4. **状态分析**:\n   - 在调用链中未出现明确的错误代码或Fast Fail情况，但显著的超时延迟（数据倍数 > 2）表明性能瓶颈。\n\n### 推理和假设验证\n1. **延迟根因判断**:\n   - 对`redis`和`cartservice-0`的延迟标明了其运行在节点`aiops-k8s-03`上，且性能显著下降。\n   - 基于`Metric 专家`提到的`node_memory_usage_rate` 和 `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes`相关耗尽问题，可以支持假设该节点资源不足导致相关Pod的性能减弱。\n\n2. **错误传播路径**:\n   - 延迟从`aiops-k8s-03`节点上的`redis`蔓延至`cartservice`，并最终传递到涉及`CartService`的外部接口。\n\n3. **Trace数据直接吻合假设**:\n   - 提出的假设明确涉及到`aiops-k8s-03`作为根因可能性，Trace数据中的延迟细节直接支持这一点，符合时间和依赖链路。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"latency_spike\", \"cartservice-0->redis\", \"aiops-k8s-03\", \"cartservice->cartservice\", \"redis latency\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-03\",\n      \"reason\": \"Node aiops-k8s-03 reported memory exhaustion, which aligns with performance degradation in redis-cart operations.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis operation HMSET had a latency spike (5.04x normal) under cartservice-0 on aiops-k8s-03.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Redis latency spike is observed, directly affecting cartservice operations.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis and cartservice traces on the same node (aiops-k8s-03) show slow response times.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
